address-list
************


Description
===========

List of addresses with a reference name. The value of an entry is a
list of IP addresses or prefixes in CIDR notation or FQDNs. The
associated key is the identifier by which the IP address list is
referenced.


Available Commands
==================

* bulk-upload

* create

* delete

* get

* list

* update

* update-address-list-update-fqdn-address-list-details

* update-address-list-update-ip-address-list-details
